We are working closely with an exciting organisation in the Energy sector to
recruit an Integration Engineer for an initial 6 month day rate contract. The
Integration Engineer will work together with internal teams to:  

  * Design, implement and maintain integration solutions 
  * Collaborate with cross-functional teams, leveraging your technical expertise in C#, microservices and Azure to enhance system connectivity and optimised data flow 
  
** Mandatory Skills/Experience: **   

  * Proficiency in C# programming language for developing integration solutions 
  * Understanding and practical expertise with microservices 
  * Azure experience: hands on experience (Azure Logic Apps, Azure Service Bus and Azure Functions) 
  * Debugging with Azure and an ability to troubleshoot integration issues using Azure tools and resources 
** Key Responsibilities and Outcomes: **   

  * Integration solution development: design, develop and implement integration solutions using C# and microservices architecture 
  * Azure Expertise - architect and deploy integration solutions 
  * Document integration solutions ensuring knowledge transfer 
